    "aaw_home_z07_fit": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"aaw-home-shell\">\n  <section class=\"aaw-home-section aaw-home-fit-section\" aria-labelledby=\"aaw-home-fit-title\">\n    <div class=\"aaw-home-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"aaw-home-section-head\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"aaw-home-kicker\">Fit before sound</p>\n          <h2 id=\"aaw-home-fit-title\">Fit first. Then the tuning can speak.</h2>\n        </div>\n        <p>Z07 is built around a stable fit because seal changes what you hear. When the monitor sits securely, bass pressure, center image, and stage focus are easier to trust.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aaw-home-proof-grid\">\n        <figure class=\"aaw-home-proof-image\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'z07-fitmorph-interchangeable-fit-options-tool.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 FitMorph holders, screws, and acoustic core\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <figcaption><b>FitMorph adaptive fit</b><span>The same acoustic core can be worn with different outer-fit holders.</span></figcaption>\n        </figure>\n        <div class=\"aaw-home-proof-list\">\n          <article><span>01</span><h3>Stable seal</h3><p>FitMorph helps more listeners find a secure seating position before judging the sound.</p></article>\n          <article><span>02</span><h3>Cleaner acoustic path</h3><p>The tubeless chamber reduces long-path pressure restrictions and filter compression.</p></article>\n          <article><span>03</span><h3>Replaceable connection</h3><p>The 0.78mm 2-pin socket is built into the replaceable FitMorph holder module.</p></article>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
