    "aaw_home_faq": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"aaw-home-shell\">\n  <section class=\"aaw-home-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"aaw-home-faq-title\">\n    <div class=\"aaw-home-wrap aaw-home-faq-grid\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"aaw-home-kicker\">FAQ</p>\n        <h2 id=\"aaw-home-faq-title\">Quick answers about AAW.</h2>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aaw-home-faq-list\">\n        <details open><summary>What does AAW specialize in?</summary><p>AAW designs and builds in-ear monitors in Singapore, including custom IEMs, universal monitors, hybrid driver designs, cables, refit work, and long-term service.</p></details>\n        <details><summary>What is the difference between universal and custom IEMs?</summary><p>Universal IEMs are ready to wear with ear tips and can be shared or resold more easily. Custom IEMs are built from your ear impressions for a personal shell shape, stronger fit security, and more design freedom.</p></details>\n        <details><summary>Do I need ear impressions for a CIEM?</summary><p>Yes. A custom in-ear monitor needs accurate ear impressions or approved digital ear scans. Good impressions help the shell seal, reduce pressure points, and lower the chance of refit work.</p></details>\n        <details><summary>Can AAW help with refits or repairs?</summary><p>Yes. AAW supports refit, warranty, repair, cable, and service questions through the Singapore office and authorized dealers. The best support contact depends on where the monitor was purchased.</p></details>\n        <details><summary>Where can I audition or order AAW?</summary><p>Visit the AAW Office at 76 Playfair Road or an authorized listening room such as Zeppelin & Co., JABEN, and AV One. Outside Singapore, use the store locator for authorized dealers.</p></details>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
